OL,5, Staff at an Amazon warehouse have      
OL,6, staged a walkout over a 35p an hour pay
OL,7, increase offer.                        
OL,9,FWorkers left the depot in Tilbury,     
OL,10,FEssex, on Wednesday and Thursday as    
OL,11,Fthey sought a rise of #2 an hour.      
OL,13,FThe GMB union said the rise asked for  
OL,14,Fwould better match the demands of the  
OL,15,Frole and help meet the cost of living  
OL,16,Fcrisis.                                
OL,18,FAmazon said its pay was "competitive"  
OL,19,Fand staff were also offered a benefits 
OL,20,Fpackage worth thousands annually.      
